<emphasis id="B976950C2779FFF9FB17C969FACFCE2A" bold="true" box="[1266,1287,1858,1881]" pageId="3" pageNumber="64">J)</emphasis>
External view of hind tibiae, showing spines. 
<emphasis id="B976950C2779FFF9FE36C94AFE26CE0B" bold="true" box="[467,494,1889,1912]" pageId="3" pageNumber="64">K)</emphasis>
