<paragraph id="8BBD491E2779FFFEFF22C98FFDADC9A7" blockId="3.[151,1436,1956,2016]" lastBlockId="4.[151,1437,151,535]" lastPageId="4" lastPageNumber="65" pageId="3" pageNumber="64">
<emphasis id="B976950C2779FFF9FF22C98FFEF2CECF" box="[199,314,1956,1980]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="64">Abdomen:</emphasis>
General color yellowish, with dark brown marks on posterior margin of each sclerite. Other dark bands are located along the dorsal and dorsolateral lines, and some small marks located in the lateral margin of each sclerite. Cerci short and the subgenital plate is not produced as it is in some species of the genus (e.g. 
<emphasis id="B976950C277EFFFEFA62CEB3FE25C9A7" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">
<taxonomicName id="4C02329D277EFFFEFA62CEB3FE98C9A7" class="Insecta" family="Lathiceridae" genus="Scapteriscus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cuadripunctatus">S. cuadripunctatus</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C02329D277EFFFEFEBECE96FE25C9A7" box="[347,493,189,212]" class="Insecta" family="Lathiceridae" genus="Scapteriscus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mexicanus">S. mexicanus</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
) (
<figureCitation id="1339559B277EFFFEFDE0CE97FD8EC9A7" box="[517,582,188,212]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,1616,1639]" captionTargetBox="[205,1394,199,1587]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[184,1403,195,1610]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Scapteriscus cerberus sp. nov. holotype male A) lateral habitus, B) Fore tibiae dactyls C) Dorsal habitus D) Timpanum. Notice the robust appearance that characterize this species. Length of scale line: 1 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/214513/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">
Fig. 
<number id="3DCA5B39277EFFFEFDDFCE97FD8EC9A7" box="[570,582,188,212]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" value="1.0">1</number>
</figureCitation>
c).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BBD491E277EFFFEFF22CECBFE26CB64" blockId="4.[151,1437,151,535]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">
<emphasis id="B976950C277EFFFEFF22CECBFE04C98B" bold="true" box="[199,460,223,248]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">Measurements (mm):</emphasis>
<specimenCount id="9D048297277EFFFEFE3CCEF4FD82C984" box="[473,586,223,247]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" type="female">
<number id="3DCA5B39277EFFFEFE3CCEF4FE2FC984" box="[473,487,223,247]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" value="2.0">2</number>
females
</specimenCount>
